%^BOLD%^GREEN%^ULINE%^Fey Bloodline%^RESET%^

The capricious nature of the fey runs in your family due to some intermingling of fey blood or magic. You are more emotional than most, prone to bouts of joy and rage.

%^GREEN%^BOLD%^Bloodline Arcana:%^RESET%^
Whenever you cast spells of the enchantment/charm sphere of magic, you gain +1 to spell DC.

%^GREEN%^BOLD%^Soul of the Fey:%^RESET%^
Your soul becomes infused with the fey, granting you poison immunity and 10 spell damage resistance.

%^GREEN%^BOLD%^Bonus Bloodline Skill%^RESET%^: survival

%^GREEN%^BOLD%^Bonus Spells%^RESET%^: dancing lights, glitterdust, phantom steed, confusion, domination, eyebite, irresistible dance, overwhelming presence
